data.title: Livro Common KADS
data.meta_description: LivroCommonKADS - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides an overview of the CommonKADS methodology for knowledge engineering and management. It discusses the importance of knowledge in the information society and introduces the CommonKADS principles, model suite, and process roles. The document is intended to guide readers through the main steps and components involved in applying the CommonKADS methodology.
